 magnetic flux features is dominated by\nconvective motion resulting from the exploding granule due to the magnetic\nfield frozen in the granular plasma. Intensification of the magnetic field\noccurs in the intergranular lanes, probably because of being directed by the\ndownflowing plasma.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2011 15:40:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Nov 2011 19:22:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2011 16:39:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-12-21"}
